title: riot grrrl compilation 05 - Mansplaining On The Dancefloor!
description:
hey everyone,

thanks to all the bands who submitted to this sampler and to everyone who sent in a cover.
we will put all covers in the zip file, but we chose the midi grrrl one as the "official cover".
anyway... by including the other ones you can decide yourself which one is your favorite.

unfortunately we didn't receive any other submissions so there is "just" music again.

so beep beep repeat:
please don't be shy and send us your designed flyer, poster, cover, text, whatever! (pdf)
as we said already... if no one is helping out with this things the compilation will NOT have anything else but music. (which is sad).
use it. it's a platform!
